{"tid":2303073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭強制半山豪宅區全部人強制檢疫未？跳舞群組確診者遍布多區豪宅，半山花園台再上榜！","createTime":"2020-11-27T15:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T12:03:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f79de2a8614f8e3ba5cb43d14918396b173bbe5","tid":2303073,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qdRoPOUSu34UDSbwBKxWMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMy4xNTc4OTQ3MzY4NDIx/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/067c1d40-307b-11eb-9ffe-d7e81f587e00\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqdRoPOUSu34UDSbwBKxWMg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMy4xNTc4OTQ3MzY4NDIx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2F067c1d40-307b-11eb-9ffe-d7e81f587e00&h=1e608d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情嚴重，昨日(26日)新增81宗確診個案，其中59宗個案屬跳舞群組，該群組已累計311人染病。根據衞生署衞生防護中心更新的確診者住宅及到訪場所名單，繼續有多個豪宅單位上榜，包括大坑豪園、薄扶林貝沙灣9座、畢架山新德園、何文田公爵閣及北角寶馬山花園8座等，西貢多個住所亦有上榜。此外，港島半山花園台第3座新增一名屬跳舞群組的住客確診，此前該處第2座已有6名住客確診，即累計7宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CHsOOOjOwdG1_h.j7kFjeQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzMDIuMTUzODQ2MTUzODQ2Mg--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/36e32aa0-307b-11eb-9ea3-3c5117dcfa34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCHsOOOjOwdG1_h.j7kFjeQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzMDIuMTUzODQ2MTUzODQ2Mg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2F36e32aa0-307b-11eb-9ea3-3c5117dcfa34&h=dd6bc7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/跳舞群組確診者遍布多區豪宅-半山花園台再上榜-063925868.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%B7%B3%E8%88%9E%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8